# Any of several [[bird]]s
##{{British}} Any of several small birds that build dome-shaped nests; the [[long-tailed tit]], [[willow warbler]] and [[chiffchaff]]
##{{US}} A [[warbler]], ''[[Seiurus auricapillus ]]'' that builds such a nest of vegetation
##(''Central America'') Any of several [[passerine]] birds that build such nests of mud

